name: PregnancyRelatedFindings
title: Pregnancy Related Findings
publisher: HL7 US Realm Program Management Steward
description: This value set contains codes to represent pregnancy related findings. It is intensionally defined as a grouping of those codes in the SNOMED CT hierarchy below 118185001 |Finding related to pregnancy (finding), those codes below 106112009 |Fetal finding (finding), and those codes below 198609003 |Complication of pregnancy, childbirth and/or the puerperium (disorder).
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains codes to represent pregnancy related findings.),(Data Element Scope: The data element represents findings that are related to a pregnancy.),(Inclusion Criteria: The grouping of those codes in the SNOMED CT hierarchy below 118185001 |Finding related to pregnancy (finding), those codes below 106112009 |Fetal finding (finding), and those codes below 198609003 |Complication of pregnancy, childbirth and/or the puerperium (disorder).),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
